# Build-context excludes (applies to backend.Dockerfile + frontend.Dockerfile,
# both built with context: .). Keeps images small and — importantly — keeps
# macOS AppleDouble (._*) cruft out of the image: alembic globs versions/*.py
# and would try to load `._<migration>.py`, which contains null bytes.

# macOS metadata
**/.DS_Store
**/._*

# VCS
.git
.gitignore

# Python
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/.venv/
**/.mypy_cache/
**/.ruff_cache/
**/.pytest_cache/

# Node / Astro
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/.astro/

# Home-lab infra reference (contains secrets) — never in a build context
homelab-josearcos-me-infra-reference.md

# Dev scratch
scripts/*.log
scripts/*.done
